    num: "01",
    title: "NonprofitOrganization and Organization schema",
    body: "Every page receives NonprofitOrganization and Organization JSON-LD markup: mission statement, cause category, geographic service area, EIN, and donation links. This tells Google exactly what your organization does and who it serves, enabling visibility in cause-specific searches and Google's Nonprofit program pathways.",
