  {
    num: "02",
    title: "GiveWP and Stripe donation integration",
    body: "We integrate GiveWP, Stripe, or your preferred donation platform directly into your site. Donors can give one-time or set up recurring gifts without leaving your domain, in a form that matches your brand. We configure donation tiers with impact descriptions, set up automatic tax receipt emails, and ensure the giving flow works on mobile, where most impulse donations happen.",
    tags: ["GiveWP / Stripe", "Recurring donations", "Tax receipt automation"],
