    tags: ["Impact storytelling", "Program pages", "Conversion copy"],
  },
  {
    num: "04",
    title: "Volunteer and event signup integration",
    body: "Beyond donations, nonprofits need volunteers and event attendees. We integrate volunteer signup forms with Volunteer Local or a custom WPForms system, and build event pages with registration capability. Every signup is connected to your email list so volunteers and attendees stay engaged with your organization's work.",
