    body: "Appearing in local search for your cause, such as 'food bank Baltimore' or 'scholarship foundation Annapolis', drives awareness and donations from people actively searching for nonprofits to support. We audit and optimize your GBP with correct nonprofit categories, service areas, and program descriptions. We also set up your Google for Nonprofits account if you haven't enrolled.",
    tags: ["Google Business Profile", "Google for Nonprofits", "Cause search SEO"],
  },
  {
    num: "06",
    title: "Core Web Vitals performance guarantee",
    body: "We guarantee your site ships with green Core Web Vitals, or we fix it before launch at no cost. Nonprofit sites with large image files, embedded social feeds, and outdated themes routinely fail these benchmarks. Donation page performance directly impacts conversion rates, so we optimize every page on the giving path using <strong>Core Web Vitals</strong> as our benchmark.",
