---
<BaseLayout
  title="Nonprofit Website Design Maryland | Upcoming Brand"
  description="Senior nonprofit website design service for NGOs, foundations, and charities. NGO schema, GiveWP / Donorbox donation integration, volunteer signup, WCAG AA accessibility, 90+ Lighthouse. Fixed-scope from $1,500."
  canonicalUrl="https://upcomingbrand.com/industries/nonprofit-website-design/"
>
  <script type="application/ld+json" set:html={JSON.stringify(schema)} slot="head" />
  <Navigation />

  <!-- ══════════════════════════════════════════════
       HERO
  ══════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
  <section class="lfh-hero">

    <div class="container">
      <nav class="lfh-breadcrumb mono-xs" aria-label="Breadcrumb">
        <a href="/">Home</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">/</span>
        <a href="/#industries">Industries</a>
        <span aria-hidden="true">/</span>
        <span>Nonprofit Website Design</span>
      </nav>
    </div>

    <div class="container lfh-wrap">

      <!-- LEFT COLUMN -->
      <div class="lfh-left">

        <div class="lfh-tags">
          <span class="lfh-pill">
            <span class="lfh-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
            Nonprofit Web Design &middot; Maryland
          </span>
          <span class="lfh-hero-sep" aria-hidden="true">&middot;</span>
          <span class="lfh-hero-eyebrow">A specialist studio, not a template shop</span>
        </div>

        <h1 class="lfh-h1">
          <span class="lfh-h1-line">Maryland nonprofit websites</span>
          <span class="lfh-h1-line lfh-h1-accent-line"><em class="lfh-h1-accent">built to drive donations</em></span>
          <span class="lfh-h1-line lfh-h1-italic">and grow your mission.</span>
        </h1>

        <p class="lfh-lede">
          Most nonprofit websites lose donors before the first gift: slow load times, broken donation forms, and copy that never explains the impact. We build WordPress sites for Maryland nonprofits that rank for cause-related searches, integrate with GiveWP or Stripe, and turn visitors into donors and volunteers. Fixed-scope from <strong>$1,500</strong>.
        </p>

        <div class="lfh-ctas">
          <a href="#contact" class="lfh-btn-primary">
            Book a discovery call
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M1 7h12M8 2l5 5-5 5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
          <a href="#pricing" class="lfh-btn-ghost">
            See pricing
            <svg width="14" height="14" viewBox="0 0 14 14" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
              <path d="M2 12L12 2M12 2H5M12 2v7" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="lfh-trust">
          <span class="lfh-trust-item">
            <svg width="12" height="12" viewBox="0 0 12 12" fill="none" aria-hidden="true"><circle cx="6" cy="6" r="5.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-opacity="0.35"/><path d="M3.5 6l2 2 3-3" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>
            Maryland-based studio
          </span>
          <span class="lfh-trust-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="lfh-trust-item">NonprofitOrganization schema on every build</span>
          <span class="lfh-trust-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="lfh-trust-item">Fixed-scope &middot; no surprises</span>
        </div>

      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT COLUMN - FORM -->
      <div class="lfh-right">
        <div class="lfh-form-card">
          <div class="lfh-form-header">
            <p class="lfh-form-eyebrow">Free site audit</p>
            <h2 class="lfh-form-title">Is your website converting visitors to donors?</h2>
            <p class="lfh-form-sub">We review your current site and send a plain-English audit within 2 business days. No sales call required.</p>
          </div>

          <form class="lfh-form" name="np-inquiry"-honeypot="bot-field" data-uc-form="np-inquiry" method="POST" novalidate>
            <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="np-inquiry" />
            <div style="position:absolute;left:-9999px;width:1px;height:1px;overflow:hidden;" aria-hidden="true">
              <label>Leave blank: <input type="text" name="bot-field" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" /></label>
            </div>

            <div class="lfh-form-row">
              <label class="lfh-form-label" for="np-name">Your name</label>
              <input class="lfh-form-input" type="text" id="np-name" name="name" placeholder="Patricia Evans" required autocomplete="name" />
            </div>

